    "description": "《宇宙鼹鼠》是一款二维收集马拉松平台游戏，你将化身背着喷射背包的鼹鼠，飞过太空各地，进入随机生成的关卡，落在不同的星球，挖掘各式各样的宝藏。探索黑洞，邂逅奇怪的生物，越过危险的障碍，发现宝贵的宝石，每次游戏的体验都不一样！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >化身宇宙鼹鼠！</h2>成为鼹鼠克莉丝，背上喷射背包，肩负使命，探索未知世界！运用她的能力飞过太空各地，落在不同的星球，发掘丰富的宝藏！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/210179729b553a7054dec5411dc8321a.poster.avif?t=1725112645\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/210179729b553a7054dec5411dc8321a.webm?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/210179729b553a7054dec5411dc8321a.mp4?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机关卡！</h2>探索宇宙太空，每次进入都会遇到不同的扭曲。星球、敌人、挑战以及宝藏的方位都会发生变化，每次都会有不同的体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/7bf91bc8bde89501dee76c6651d7b8fe.poster.avif?t=1725112645\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/7bf91bc8bde89501dee76c6651d7b8fe.webm?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/7bf91bc8bde89501dee76c6651d7b8fe.mp4?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >获得所有宝藏！</h2>潜入宇宙异象造成的黑洞，寻找各式各样的宝贝。每一颗宝石和珍稀物品都能助你继续深入，发现更多未知空间！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/2ec43730e17a473651cb5b6a9f53aa4c.poster.avif?t=1725112645\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/2ec43730e17a473651cb5b6a9f53aa4c.webm?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/2ec43730e17a473651cb5b6a9f53aa4c.mp4?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >难题无处不在！</h2>宇宙异象的黑洞之中，多种难题随处可见，都会考验你作为宇宙鼹鼠的能力。克服这些难题，就能获得星辰宝石，这是最为珍贵的宝贝，也只有这种东西能够解锁异象更深处的秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/fdf8ceb4872643c68cd803f1d2f1c755.poster.avif?t=1725112645\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/fdf8ceb4872643c68cd803f1d2f1c755.webm?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/fdf8ceb4872643c68cd803f1d2f1c755.mp4?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >鼹鼠升级项目！</h2>带着宝石、星石和图纸去见克莉丝的姐姐康蒂（也是常驻鼹鼠机师）。她会用这些东西给克莉丝的装备和能力升级，还会破解图纸，了解新的鼹鼠招式。克莉丝了解这些之后，就能更加深入黑洞，找到更多宝藏了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/10ad6cca8a375252e6219fbb2391b3e8.poster.avif?t=1725112645\" width=590 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/10ad6cca8a375252e6219fbb2391b3e8.webm?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094940/extras/10ad6cca8a375252e6219fbb2391b3e8.mp4?t=1725112645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
